# Access Control Policy

**Company:** {{ company.name }}
**Scope:** All information systems and personnel.
**Last Reviewed:** {{ today }}

## Purpose
To ensure that only authorized users have access to systems and data required for their roles.

## Policy
- Access is granted on the principle of least privilege and role-based access control.
- Joiners/Movers/Leavers are processed within 24 hours of HR notification.
- Access reviews occur **{{ controls.access_review_frequency }}** by the system owners and are documented.

## Authentication
- MFA is required for all privileged accounts and remote access.
- Passwords comply with NIST SP 800-63B and are rotated when compromised.

## Monitoring
- All access events are logged and retained for at least {{ retention.years }} years.